We are adding a new project to your bucket for the DS Analyzer enhancement. As part of this initiative, we will introduce support for custom mitigation methods and rules that are specific to each product. Since every product has its own table names and sanitization methods, the DS Analyzer prompt must be enhanced to dynamically incorporate these product-specific configurations. This will ensure that the analyzer applies the appropriate mitigation logic and sanitization process based on the respective product context, resulting in more accurate and scalable analysis.

Currently, this functionality is available only for EMR. At this stage, the auto-posting of comments and the auto-attachment of Stride Excel threads to Jira have been enabled exclusively for PE projects within this block.